lead_paragraph: Chris Seitz made his only save in the 72nd minute and FC Dallas won the first Supporters' Shield in franchise history with a scoreless draw against the Los Angeles Galaxy on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: FC Dallas Wins Supporters' Shield in 0-0 Draw With Galaxy
